Developer Terms of Use
des:
White Meditation is the Alexa skill that offers guided meditation sessions whenever you need them. With over 10 meditations to choose from, calming voices, and soothing background sounds, this skill is designed to help both your body and mind relax and find peace.

Meditation sessions are available in various lengths: 10, 20, or 30 minutes.

Unlock Pro Features to enjoy:

• Professional meditation voices
• A wide selection of background sounds perfect for your sessions
• Unlimited access with no restrictions
• Regularly updated meditation programs
• Full access to all session durations

We’d love to hear your feedback to keep improving and provide the best guided meditation experience.

Relax and enjoy your meditation!
